Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.39,0:21:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.06,0:21:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但..這又是真實的嗎？
